    <item>
      <title>特朗普的美国比特币储备计划引起没收专家的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/trump-s-plan-for-us-bitcoin-stockpile-alarms-forfeiture-experts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在竞选时承诺利用美国政府持有的加密货币建立国家比特币储备，这引起了前检察官的担忧，他们表示，此举将转移扣押的数字资产，而这些资产原本可用于补偿犯罪受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/trump-s-plan-for-us-bitcoin-stockpile-alarms-forfeiture-experts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日尔因涉嫌支持马里叛军而与乌克兰断绝关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/niger-cuts-ties-with-ukraine-over-its-alleged-backing-of-malian-rebels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日尔军政府与马里一道，因乌克兰涉嫌支持马里叛军而断绝了与乌克兰的外交关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/niger-cuts-ties-with-ukraine-over-its-alleged-backing-of-malian-rebels</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:52:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>要求延长津巴布韦领导人执政的竞选活动势头强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/campaign-to-extend-zimbabwean-leader-s-rule-gains-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦表示，他打算在 2028 年第二任期结束时下台，但执政党内部要求他再任两年的呼声日益高涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/campaign-to-extend-zimbabwean-leader-s-rule-gains-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦驱逐袭击首相的波兰男子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/denmark-deports-polish-man-after-attack-on-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名波兰男子因在哥本哈根街头袭击丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森，被丹麦一家法院判处驱逐出境和四个月监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/denmark-deports-polish-man-after-attack-on-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:29:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯新政治领袖辛瓦尔有着狡猾而残暴的过去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/hamas-new-political-chief-sinwar-has-a-cunning-and-brutal-past</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大约六年前，刚刚被任命为​​哈马斯政治领袖的叶海亚·辛瓦尔在一份文件上潦草地写了一张便条，他知道埃及中间人会将这份文件交给以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/hamas-new-political-chief-sinwar-has-a-cunning-and-brutal-past</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:15:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国被罢免的领导人哈西娜的儿子表示她不会再回来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bangladesh-s-ousted-leader-sheikh-hasina-won-t-return-son-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谢赫·哈西娜在针对其统治的激烈抗议中于本周辞去总理职务并逃离孟加拉国，她不打算返回这个由她的家人共同打造的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bangladesh-s-ousted-leader-sheikh-hasina-won-t-return-son-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:10:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京指责乌克兰因俄罗斯入侵而“挑衅”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/death-toll-rises-as-russia-battles-border-incursion-from-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·普京指责乌克兰向俄罗斯库尔斯克地区派遣数百名士兵，进行“大规模挑衅”，这是自他于 2022 年下令入侵邻国以来对俄罗斯领土发动的最大规模攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/death-toll-rises-as-russia-battles-border-incursion-from-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:55:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院因反对王室改革而解散反对党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thai-court-set-to-decide-fate-of-thailand-s-most-popular-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最高法院以违反选举规则为由下令解散该国最大的反对党，这一判决有可能引发这个东南亚国家新的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/thai-court-set-to-decide-fate-of-thailand-s-most-popular-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
